---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/sections/Section.astro';
import CTABanner from '../../components/sections/CTABanner.astro';
import Card from '../../components/ui/Card.astro';
import Button from '../../components/ui/Button.astro';
import ScrollReveal from '../../components/animation/ScrollReveal.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Prove It — Challenge Everything You've Heard | IBC Academy"
  description="You've heard IBC is a scam, a ripoff, or just overpriced whole life insurance. Good. Read these 6 articles and see if your position holds up."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Section background="cream">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="hero-eyebrow">For the Skeptics</span>
        <h1 class="hero-title">You Think This Is a Scam. <br />We Think You Should Prove It.</h1>
        <p class="hero-text">
          You've done your homework. You've heard Dave Ramsey call it "a load of manure." Your financial advisor told you whole life is a terrible investment. Suze Orman said to stay away. The internet is full of people who agree with you.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-text">
          And you know what? They're not entirely wrong.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-text">
          The insurance industry has earned your distrust. Bad products. Bad actors. Bad advice dressed up in nice suits. Most of what's sold as "whole life insurance" deserves the criticism it gets.
        </p>
        <p class="hero-text">
          But here's the thing about being right on the surface — it can make you wrong underneath. And if you're as analytical as you think you are, six articles shouldn't scare you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- What This Is (And Isn't) -->
  <Section title="What This Journey Is (And Isn't)">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="clarity-content">
        <div class="clarity-grid">
          <div class="clarity-box">
            <h3 class="clarity-heading is-not">This is NOT:</h3>
            <ul class="clarity-list">
              <li>A sales pitch disguised as education</li>
              <li>Emotional manipulation or fear tactics</li>
              <li>A claim that whole life "beats the market"</li>
              <li>An attack on your intelligence</li>
              <li>A defense of the insurance industry</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="clarity-box">
            <h3 class="clarity-heading is-yes">This IS:</h3>
            <ul class="clarity-list">
              <li>Data, math, and sourced claims you can verify</li>
              <li>An honest look at what critics get right — and wrong</li>
              <li>The arguments your advisor never addressed</li>
              <li>A challenge: read all six and see if your position holds</li>
              <li>Permission to change your mind — or walk away confident</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="clarity-footer">
          If you're right, these articles will confirm it. If you're wrong, wouldn't you want to know?
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- The 6 Articles -->
  <Section title="The 6-Article Challenge" subtitle="Each article takes 5–7 minutes. Sources cited. Math shown. No hand-waving." background="cream">
    <div class="journey-grid">
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={0}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/prove-it-01-right-to-be-skeptical" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">01</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">You're Right to Be Skeptical</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">The insurance industry has earned your distrust. Bad products, bad actors, bad advice. Here's what they got wrong — and what they accidentally got right.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={100}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/prove-it-02-rate-of-return-trap" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">02</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">The Rate of Return Trap</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">You've been trained to ask "What's the rate of return?" It's the wrong question. Nelson Nash asked a better one: "Compared to what?"</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={200}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/prove-it-03-dave-ramsey" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">03</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">What Dave Ramsey Gets Wrong (And Right)</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">"Buy term and invest the difference" sounds logical. But does the math actually work? Let's run the numbers Dave never shows you.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={300}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/prove-it-04-advisor-hates-whole-life" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">04</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">Why Your Financial Advisor Hates Whole Life</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">It's not a conspiracy. It's an incentive structure. Understanding why they say what they say changes everything.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={400}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/prove-it-05-math-nobody-shows" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">05</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">The Math Nobody Shows You</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">Wade Pfau, Robert Murphy, and decades of actuarial data tell a different story than the one you've heard. Here are the real numbers.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal direction="up" delay={500}>
        <a href="/learn/articles/prove-it-06-everything-you-heard" class="journey-card-link">
          <div class="journey-card">
            <span class="journey-number">06</span>
            <h3 class="journey-title">What If Everything You Heard Was Wrong?</h3>
            <p class="journey-desc">You came here to debunk IBC. By now, you've seen the data. The question isn't whether whole life works. It's whether you're willing to reconsider.</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Why Bother -->
  <Section title="Why Bother?">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="why-content">
        <p class="why-text">
          Here's what's interesting about your position:
        </p>
        <blockquote class="why-quote">
          "When Dave gets emotional, he gets sloppy. When he gets sloppy, he gets things wrong. Not opinions — facts. Checkable, Google-able facts."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="why-attribution">— from Article 3 of this series</p>
        <p class="why-text">
          Most critics of whole life insurance are repeating arguments they've never actually tested. They heard a confident person say it, it sounded right, and they moved on.
        </p>
        <p class="why-text">
          That's not skepticism. That's trust with extra steps.
        </p>
        <p class="why-text">
          Real skepticism means checking both sides. If the case against IBC is as airtight as you believe, six articles won't change your mind. But if there are cracks in the argument — wouldn't you want to find them before you build your financial life on top of them?
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <Section background="cream">
    <ScrollReveal direction="up">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Still Think It's a Scam?</h2>
        <p class="cta-text">
          Prove it. Start with Article 1. We'll even agree with you for the first few paragraphs.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-button">
          <Button variant="primary" size="lg" href="/learn/articles/prove-it-01-right-to-be-skeptical">
            Begin the Challenge →
          </Button>
        </div>
        <p class="cta-note">
          No signup. No email capture. No pitch at the end. Just data you can verify yourself.
        </p>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </Section>

  <!-- Final Note -->
  <CTABanner
    heading="Have Questions? Bring Your Best Arguments."
    description="Join our free community where skeptics and practitioners go back and forth. Ask the hard questions. We're not afraid of them."
    buttonText="Join the Conversation"
    buttonHref="https://skool.com/ibc-academy"
  />
</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #EF4444;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .hero-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .hero-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Clarity Section */
  .clarity-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .clarity-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .clarity-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .clarity-box {
    background: var(--color-cream, #FAF9F6);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .clarity-heading {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .clarity-heading.is-not {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
  }

  .clarity-heading.is-yes {
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
  }

  .clarity-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .clarity-list li {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .clarity-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #EF4444;
  }

  .clarity-footer {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Journey Section */
  .journey-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .journey-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .journey-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .journey-card-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .journey-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(27, 42, 74, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
  }

  .journey-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(27, 42, 74, 0.12);
  }

  .journey-number {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #EF4444;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .journey-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .journey-desc {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Why Section */
  .why-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
  }

  .why-quote {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem 0;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid #EF4444;
    text-align: left;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .why-quote {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }
  }

  .why-attribution {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    text-align: left;
    padding-left: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .why-attribution {
      padding-left: 2rem;
    }
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-navy, #1B2A4A);
    margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
  }

  .cta-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
  }

  .cta-button {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-note {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary, #5A6B8A);
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
